citation: Auctioneers and Real Estate Agents Amendment Act 2001 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Auctioneers and Real Estate Agents Amendment Act 2001 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Auctioneers and Real Estate Agents Amendment Act 2001 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
